1. Find the average score: 
promt the user to enter 10 exam scores 
store each test score into variables e.g escore1, score2... 
calculate the sum of the scores(sum score1, + score2 + score3 + ...) 
divide the sum by 10 
display de result to the user 



2.How much water runs off the roof: 
promt the user to enter the dimensions of the footprint of the roof 
store the dimensions into a variable 
convert the dimensions into inches and store the result into a variable (e.g result1)
multiply result1 by the number of inches (1") and store the result into another variable (e.g result2)
divide result2 by 231 to get the number of gallons 
Now display the gallons result to the user 



